Well,they don't know what to think.

101
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:56,960
But,you know there's a case in New Jersey a couple of years back...

102
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,460
a teenage kid put antifreeze in his parents' iced tea.

103
