Turned out he was pissed off about being grounded.

104
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:05,630
Listen,Emily,the truth is,

105
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:08,100
lots of kids get angry at their parents.

106
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:11,230
Look... if your folks

107
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:13,760
are mistreating you or abusing you,

108
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:16,630
mentally,emotionally... even physically,

109
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:18,200
it could count in your favor.

110
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:20,000
Tell me the truth about everything you know,

111
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:22,060
and it could go a long way towards

112
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:23,530
