113
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:28,830
Excuse me,uh,but we're busy here,

114
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,360
if you don't mind,huh?

115
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:33,160
I do mind. You shouldn't be in the same room with this patient,

116
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:36,130
not without adequate protection.

117
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,000
What do you mean," protection" ?

118
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:39,160
She's carrying

119
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:41,730
