174
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:14,100
Well,nothing in here looks all that dangerous.

175
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:17,900
Be that as it may,we've got a sample size of four subjects,

176
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:20,000
three who ate breakfast and got sick,

177
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:22,960
and one who ate the same breakfast and didn't get sick.

178
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:25,230
Make that a sample size of five.

179
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:27,330
Looks like they have a dog.

180
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:58,400
- Hey,Eddie.  - Hey,Mom.

181
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,960
- Hey,son.  - Brought the mail up.

