213
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:23,130
Because dogs metabolize toxins much faster than we do.

214
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,630
Look.

215
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:28,660
Single mass...

216
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:32,030
